ivardefs.name: description
ivardefs.desc: A human-readable description of the alternative explaining when the alternative should occur rather than the base step.

ivardefs.name: title
ivardefs.desc: The label to display for the alternative that gives a sense of the circumstance in which the alternative should be invoked.

properties.desc: Indicates an alternative step that can be taken instead of the operations on the base step in exceptional/atypical circumstances.
